              <div class="vendor-tier"><span class="tier-name">Enterprise</span> — ~€151/gebruiker (€165)</div>
              <div class="vendor-tier"><span class="tier-name">Unlimited</span> — ~€275/gebruiker (€300)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
